callee: Database->SELECT "atk_barang_atk"."id", "atk_barang_atk"."atk", "atk_barang_atk"."keterangan", "atk_barang_atk"."kategori_id", "atk_barang_atk"."satuan_id", "atk_barang_atk"."jumlah_per_satuan", "atk_barang_atk"."updated", "atk_barang_atk"."created" FROM "atk_barang_atk" ORDER BY "atk_barang_atk"."updated" DESC, "atk_barang_atk"."created" DESC LIMIT 21

Database->SELECT "atk_isi_pengajuan"."id", "atk_isi_pengajuan"."pengajuan_id", "atk_isi_pengajuan"."atk_id", "atk_isi_pengajuan"."jumlah", "atk_isi_pengajuan"."rekomendasi", "atk_isi_pengajuan"."keterangan", "atk_isi_pengajuan"."perbaikan", "atk_isi_pengajuan"."updated", "atk_isi_pengajuan"."created" FROM "atk_isi_pengajuan" WHERE "atk_isi_pengajuan"."pengajuan_id" = 8 ORDER BY "atk_isi_pengajuan"."updated" DESC, "atk_isi_pengajuan"."created" DESC LIMIT 21

Database->SELECT "atk_jadwal"."id", "atk_jadwal"."tahun", "atk_jadwal"."pengajuan_mulai", "atk_jadwal"."pengajuan_selesai", "atk_jadwal"."status", "atk_jadwal"."keterangan", "atk_jadwal"."updated", "atk_jadwal"."created" FROM "atk_jadwal" WHERE "atk_jadwal"."tahun" = 2023 ORDER BY "atk_jadwal"."updated" DESC, "atk_jadwal"."created" DESC LIMIT 1

Database->SELECT "atk_pengajuan"."id", "atk_pengajuan"."jadwal_id", "atk_pengajuan"."unit_id", "atk_pengajuan"."no_surat", "atk_pengajuan"."keterangan", "atk_pengajuan"."progress", "atk_pengajuan"."hasil", "atk_pengajuan"."perbaikan", "atk_pengajuan"."is_terlambat", "atk_pengajuan"."is_aktif", "atk_pengajuan"."updated", "atk_pengajuan"."created" FROM "atk_pengajuan" WHERE ("atk_pengajuan"."jadwal_id" = 8 AND "atk_pengajuan"."unit_id" = 1) ORDER BY "atk_pengajuan"."updated" DESC, "atk_pengajuan"."created" DESC LIMIT 1
